d:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Brandmark is best suited for solopreneurs, quick branding, MVP launches, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Looka, meanwhile, shines for startups, entrepreneurs, small businesses, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2017, Brandmark describes itself as \"AI logo design tool that creates unique brand identities in seconds.\" Looka, established in 2016, positions itself as \"AI-powered logo maker and brand identity design platform.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
e:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Looka** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (7.0 vs 6.0), more features (5 vs 3), more competitive pricing. However, this does not mean Brandmark is a poor choice — far from it. Brandmark excels in its own right, particularly for solopreneurs and quick branding.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value quick ai-generated logo options, go with Looka. If fast ai logo generation matters more to you, Brandmark is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
